<D>__{want a ride home?}
<C>__{catch}
<D>__{oh, thanks, but... i like to walk.}
<C>__{sharon}
<D>__{it's starting to rain. don't be a hero.}
<A>__{he hesitates, nervous about it, but then...}
<C>__{catch}
<D>__{yeah. if it's no trouble. thanks.}
<A>__{they walk to her car.}
